<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.7.6">
<l>aḷikkum paramaṉaik kaṇṇaṉai yāḻip pirāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>tuḷikku naṟuṅkaṇṇit tūmaṇi vaṇṇaṉem māṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>yoḷikoṇṭa cōtiyai yuḷḷattuk koḷḷu mavarkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>calippiṉṟi yāṇṭemmaic caṉmacaṉ māntaraṅ kāpparē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those, see, who take into [their] hearts the bright effulgence,</l>
<l>the Highest one who takes care, Kṛṣṇa, the lord with the discus,</l>
<l>our lord with the colour of the pure sapphire with a [nectar-]dripping fragrant chaplet</l>
<l>will without weariness rule [and] guard us in birth after birth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
